<tr>
<td colspan="2" style="line-height:150%; padding:0.8em 1.0em 0.2em 1.5em; border-top: 1px #aaa solid; text-align:left; font-size:80%; font-weight:lighter;"><span style="margin:0.5em; color:#555;">* Not meant as a <a href="/wiki/Posek" title="Posek">definitive ruling</a>. Some <a href="/wiki/Mitzvah" title="Mitzvah">observances</a> may be <a href="/wiki/Rabbinical_literature" title="Rabbinical literature" class="mw-redirect">rabbinical</a>, or <a href="/wiki/Minhag" title="Minhag">customs</a>, or <a href="/wiki/Torah" title="Torah">Torah</a> based.</span></td>
